name: Omnisea
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Omnichain Router - Our core contract connects multiple cross-chain messaging protocols such as LayerZero and Axelar Network.
Omnisea NFT Launchpad - using our Omnichain Router, we provide ability to easily launch Omnichain NFTs collections and mint between chains - we're currently supporting Ethereum, BNB Chain, Polygon, Avalanche, Optimism, Arbitrum, and Fantom.

OSEA is our omnichain ERC-20 Token built using LayerZero contracts. Available on Polygon (base, total supply controller), Ethereum, BNB Chain, Avalanche, Fantom, Optimism, and Arbitrum.
